<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Your Dnyanpith code</title>
  <style>
    body { font-family: 'DM Sans', Arial, sans-serif; background: #F8F4EF; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    .wrapper { max-width: 520px; margin: 40px auto; background: #fff; border-radius: 8px; overflow: hidden; }
    .header { background: #1A3C5E; padding: 24px 32px; }
    .header h1 { color: #F8F4EF; font-size: 22px; font-weight: 300; margin: 0; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
    .header h1 span { color: #D4A017; font-style: italic; }
    .body { padding: 32px; color: #2D2D2D; font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; }
    .code { font-size: 36px; font-weight: 600; letter-spacing: 0.2em; color: #1A3C5E;
            background: #f0ebe3; border-radius: 6px; padding: 16px 24px;
            display: inline-block; margin: 16px 0; }
    .expiry { color: #5a6e7a; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 8px; }
    .footer { padding: 20px 32px; border-top: 1px solid #f0ebe3; color: #5a6e7a; font-size: 12px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="wrapper">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Dnyanpith<span> ·</span></h1>
    </div>
    <div class="body">
      <p>Hi{{#if name}} {{name}}{{/if}},</p>
      <p>Your sign-in code is:</p>
      <div class="code">{{code}}</div>
      <p class="expiry">This code expires in {{expiryMinutes}} minutes. Do not share it with anyone.</p>
      <p>If you did not request this code, you can ignore this email.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      Dnyanpith Abhyasika Pvt. Ltd. · Ambajogai, Maharashtra
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
